[[!img "bitcoin_wallet.png" size=192x192]]

An open-source and free Android implementation of a Bitcoin Wallet, based on [[bitcoinj|BitCoinJ]]. It was released on March 7, 2011 (1.1). A build for BlackBerry OS is available, too.

##External Links

* [(1)](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.schildbach.wallet) Bitcoin Wallet on Google Play.
* [(2)](https://appworld.blackberry.com/webstore/content/23952882/) Bitcoin Wallet on BlackBerry World.
* [(3)](https://code.google.com/p/bitcoin-wallet/downloads/list) direct download of test versions
* [(4)](https://code.google.com/p/bitcoin-wallet/) project page on Google Code.
* [(5)](https://github.com/schildbach/bitcoin-wallet) project page on Github.
* [(6)](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?board=100.0) discussion forum on Bitcointalk

